</h3>
  

      
            <div class="field field--name-field-position field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item">Operating Executive</div>
      
  
  <button class="bio-more js-bio-more"><span class="visually-hidden">Read more about <span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden">David L. Squier</span>
</span></button>
