<p><span><span><span><span>Vilandrie most recently served as Co-Founder and Managing Partner of Altman Vilandrie &amp; Company (now Altman Solon following a July 2020 merger with European partner Solon Management Consulting), which has been widely known as one of the leading telecommunications, media, and technology-focused strategy consulting firms globally. Vilandrie has advised many c-suite and senior TMT executives and investors within the digital infrastructure industry from a strategic, go-to-market, M&amp;A, and business model perspective. Prior to Altman Vilandrie, he served as vice president at Cambridge Strategic Management Group. </span></span></span></span></p>
